werkschaftlichen Handelns. Im Fokus stehen gewerkschaftliche Kontakte vor 1989, die Phasen von Umbruch und Vereinigung, die Arbeit der Treuhandanstalt und die Tarifpolitik. Herausgearbeitet werden dabei auch die Nachwirkungen des Transformationsprozesses.  aNot much notice has been taken of the part unions have been playing in the social and economical transformation of East Germany yet. This volume explores successes and limitations of union activities in those days.  afunded by Hans-Böckler-Stiftung  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aArbeit. 4aArbeits- und Industriesoziologie. 4aArbeitsökonomie. 4aDeutsche Einheit. 4aGeschichtswissenschaft. 4aOstdeutschland. 4aPolitik. 4aSozialpolitik. 4aTarifpolitik. 4aTransformation. 4aTreuhandanstalt. 4aZeitgeschichte. 7aHISTORY / Modern / 20th Century.2bisacsh  aCollective Bargaining.  aContemporary History.  aEastern Germany.  aGerman Unity.  aHistory.  aLabour Economics.  aPolitics.  aSocial Policy.  aSociology of Work and Industry.  aTransformation.  aWork.1 aArtus, Ingrid, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBrunner, Detlev, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBrunner, Detlev, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aBöick, Marcus, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHürtgen, Renate, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aIssen, Roland, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKuhnhenne, Michaela, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKuhnhenne, Michaela, eed